WWW-Yandex-Catalog-LookupSite

This module retrieves a website's Thematic Index of Citing, checks 
website's presence in Yandex Catalog, retrieves it's descriptions 
as recorded in the catalog, and the list of categories it belongs to.

This module uses LWP::UserAgent for making requests to Yandex Catalog.


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install


SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc WWW::Yandex::Catalog::LookupSite

You can also look for information at:

    GitHub Repository
        https://github.com/OpossumPetya/WWW-Yandex-Catalog-LookupSite

    MetaCPAN
        https://metacpan.org/module/WWW::Yandex::Catalog::LookupSite

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/WWW-Yandex-Catalog-LookupSite/


